{"tid":790760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際突發】刀手巴黎市郊施襲 釀至少一死兩重傷","createTime":"2018-08-23T09:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T10:06:50.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f0c563b085123c42cadbcf03c135b203ed1bd66","tid":790760,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:18:04.000Z","msg":"外電引述法國警方消息報道，一名刀手在巴黎市郊特拉普（Trappes）施襲，導致最少一死兩重傷，初步消息指，涉案刀手已被保安部隊擊斃，目前警方的行動已經結束。<br />\n有報道指，該名刀手是向途人施襲，並在襲擊時高叫「真主偉大」。刀手行兇後曾在一間屋內匿藏，其後被警方擊斃。<br />\n路透社／美聯社／今日俄羅斯  <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180823/58598431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180823%2F58598431&d=t1PXMhj4yW7L02zRJ6hr9r%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=b9dc2263\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180823%2F58598431&h=952d4053\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180823/58598431</a>"},{"pid":"c967cf7433bbd19f7e3c8ddda32004b34513a9ae","tid":790760,"uid":168698,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"家下巴黎已經唔係巴黎，周圍都係垃圾同難民，<br />\n<br />\n好多法國女人都選擇留係屋企，<br />\n<br />\n巴黎大大話話都有一百間清真寺，一講法國萬歲即刻被難民黑社會打，<br />\n<br />\n很多cafe被難民劃為伊斯蘭區唔被法國人入去，中東難民投票支持左翼高達八十百分比"},{"pid":"25356365d830ce89cd7b2dec3d8c182fce43c994","tid":790760,"uid":168698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:37:53.000Z","msg":"如果大家想學英文看歐洲時事可以看Paul Joseph Watson，不過家下人地被YouTube封殺緊"},{"pid":"67b1e95b387fd3528e44d03c95881ea90484b836","tid":790760,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:42:17.000Z","msg":"又係回教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47771c8dfba7096fcf8df1c7c14baf3b18f9c97","tid":790760,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:49:19.000Z","msg":"法國幾時玩完"},{"pid":"6f0326dfc95f4d7a4f1f7a45576e46a52704849d","tid":790760,"uid":168698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T10:06:50.000Z","msg":"恭喜法蘭西斯坦立國"}]}